Subject: Back at the base


> ::KitKat::
>
> Finally makes it back to Destructor's base.  "Destructor, please see
> to it that the others have rooms.  If there isn't enough space, you
> may give my room to someone.  Right now, I care not where I sleep. I
> will be in the lab if anyone needs me." She turned to
> Drillbit,"Please help him find the space for everyone. I have a lot
> work ahead of me."  She opens her hip compartment and pulls out the
> spark.  She walked down the hall looking at the spark. She still
> couldn't beleive that is was a clone spark and not a real one. She
> walked into the lab and sets the spark in a containment jar.  Walks
> to the console across the room and presses a few buttons on the
> panel.  A blue light shines down on the spark and starts to sort out
> the componants of the spark.  She presses another set of buttons and
> a small red beam starts to cut the spark into several pieces.  She
> presses the third set of buttons and small green beam starts to
> analize the DNA, cellular structure and molecular composition.  She
> let the computer work and sat in a chair near the console.  She propt
> her arm up and rested her head in her hand.  She was still very mad
> about the fact that she had killed a clone and not the real Megatron.
>
